summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 73E, page 174, of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in South 1/2 of North 1/2 of Northeast 1/4 Southeast 1/4 of Northeast 1/4 of Section 27-24-4 located on east side Rainier Ave. between Willow and Holly St. as Multiple Residence (RM) Zone.
